Texts.Chs: 一本叶族烹饪书。以无数食谱为特色，全都是肉食性的。每一道菜都对应着不同的有知觉的物种。这导致它被禁止在守护团的大多数星区流传。
Texts.Eng: A Floran cook-book. It features a myriad of recipes, all carnivorous in nature. Each recipe section corresponds to a different sentient species. This has resulted in it being banned from the majority of Protectorate space.
